		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I recall when you told a variant of this story in your Entrepreneurship class. I believe it serves as a good anecdotal reminder that as Humans our interaction with computers is still very new and unexplored. There are may be &#8216;unsolvable&#8217; problems, how we attempt to solve them might teach us something even more valuable than having a solution.</p>
